00:27:11.680 --> 00:27:12.640
You kid

00:27:12.759 --> 00:27:14.400
You almost angered your mom to death

00:27:14.880 --> 00:27:16.839
How is your mom's health now?

00:27:17.960 --> 00:27:18.920
My mom is just

00:27:21.799 --> 00:27:23.079
