00:27:26.000 --> 00:27:26.559
So much energy

00:27:26.759 --> 00:27:27.799
Strength to move mountains

00:27:27.880 --> 00:27:28.839
Strong as an ox

00:27:30.680 --> 00:27:31.640
A powerhouse, my god

