I'm helping my mom find... find something

00:27:38.039 --> 00:27:38.559
Find what?

00:27:38.960 --> 00:27:39.440
Find

00:27:40.279 --> 00:27:40.920
Find some

00:27:41.480 --> 00:27:42.079
Is it

00:27:42.480 --> 00:27:43.440
what I asked your mom

00:27:43.440 --> 00:27:44.839
