Don't move

00:28:08.039 --> 00:28:08.519
Right here

00:28:08.519 --> 00:28:09.279
Don't move, don't move

00:28:09.319 --> 00:28:10.839
Let me dig, dig, dig

00:28:11.440 --> 00:28:12.000
See? Isn't it?

00:28:12.160 --> 00:28:12.640
Don't move

00:28:14.519 --> 00:28:16.079
What are you doing? You kid

00:28:16.200 --> 00:28:17.440
I spent all morning on this

00:28:17.440 --> 00:28:18.920
Why are you pulling it out?

00:28:18.920 --> 00:28:19.599
All morning

00:28:19.599 --> 00:28:20.519
I forgot what my mom wanted

00:28:20.519 --> 00:28:21.279
I'll ask her later. No, you...

00:28:21.640 --> 00:28:22.680
Auntie Niu, didn't you...

